            <head>Biographical Note</head>
            <p>Tullio Pinelli, born 1908 in Turin, Italy, was a sriptwriter who is well-known for
                his work on films by Italian filmmaker Federico Fellini. Pinelli helped to write
                more than seventy films, including classics such as <emph render="italic">I
                    vitelloni,</emph>
                <emph render="italic">La strada,</emph>
                <emph render="italic">La Dolce Vita,</emph> and <emph render="italic">8 1/2.</emph>
                He died in Rome in 2009.</p>
